mobile_circles.circle_name: Gujarat (includes Daman and Diu, Dadra and Nagar Haveli)
West Bengal (includes Andaman and Nicobar Islands, Sikkim excludes Calcutta Telecom District)
Kolkata Metro (includes parts of Howrah, Hooghly, North and South 24 Parganas and Nadia Districts)
North East India (includes Arunachal Pradesh, Meghalaya, Mizoram, Nagaland, Manipur and Tripura)
Tamil Nadu (excludes CH Chennai, MEPZ, Mahabalipuram and Minjur and includes Puducherry except Yanam and Mahe), Chennai Metro (includes MEPZ,Mahabalipuram & Minjur)
Delhi Metro (includes NCR, Faridabad, Ghaziabad, Gurgaon and Noida)
Andhra Pradesh (includes Telangana and Yanam district also)
Uttar Pradesh (West) and Uttarakhand (excludes Ghaziabad and Noida)
Maharashtra (includes Goa but excludes Mumbai, Navi Mumbai and Kalyan)
Mumbai Metro (includes Navi Mumbai and Kalyan)
